reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I had needed a replacement for my 10-year-old camera, but didn't know which one to buy! I finally decided to go with this one, an "Amazon Choice" and am so pleased with it. It sits very steadily on my monitor. The picture is excellent. The color is fabulous! And it is easily adjustable as it sits on the monitor to focus straight ahead, down or up! I seldom write reviews, but when I find a product that really is effective, I'm delighted to do so! In addition, there is a sliding "door" over the camera so when not it is not in use it can easily be closed. Great product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A very good and easy to use webcam
reviews.reviewText: It auto-installed very quickly on my Windows10 desktop. The resolution is incredibly sharp, most definitely better than my on-board webcam that my laptop has, and the auto-focus works quickly and well as I move closer and further away from the camera. The microphones do a great job picking up sound and I'm heard clearly by others. I would highly recommend this device.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Poor quality picture
reviews.reviewText: I needed a webcam and decided to stick with the brand my sister purchased. Apparently this was the latest model from the one she bought. The setup was simple however the quality was grainy and it took some time for the picture to become focused. My son put a blue candy in front of the cam to show my sister and the video became temporarily blue. The older version seems to be better than the new one. However, I liked the look of this smaller one compared to hers. I may have got a defective one but plan to send it band and purchase a different brand due to quality of picture.UPDATE: After writing my initial 1 star review I can gladly say I’ll change it to 5 stars. Immediately following my review their customer service contacted me for details. They offered a full refund but I decided to take another chance on it so they send me a replacement. Definitely was a faulty camera I received but this new one was exactly what I expected. Thank you!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Decent camera for a good price
reviews.reviewText: This camera was a bit of an upgrade from my old one. The clarity is better and the sound clear. Good for daily use. For the price, it is a well made camera and overall I am pretty happy with the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Another solid TeckNet product
reviews.reviewText: I’ve bought a few products from TeckNet over the years (computermice, usb dongles, headphones, etc) and they were all excellent. This camera did not disappoint.I use it with MS Teams and the picture quality is clear, no lag, properly colored/saturated, crisp. For legal reasons, I cannot provide a photo of this being used live on Teams. Apologies on that.Install was plug and play. Teams recognized the device immediately. Super easy. My monitor has a rounded back, and while it wasn’t a flush fit the camera does mount securely.The cord on this is longer than expected, but it came w a nice, velcro cable tie so it was easy to keep it tidy.All in all, I really like this camera and will continue to purchase products from TeckNet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Picture is Grainy
reviews.reviewText: I really wanted to like this camera as it is a great price but the picture quality is grainy which is a real disappointment. I was hoping that this would be a solution for work but not sure it is going to work for me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars less than worthless
reviews.reviewText: Did not work and then just caused problems with my New Computer. Had to trouble shoot with Dell, which is not a short episode.Time consuming when you are just about to have a meeting.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Wide Angel View
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to upgrade my desktop webcam, and the TECKNET 1080P did that easily. It was simple plug and play on my Windows 11 desktop. My old VX-1000 Webcam was only 640 X 480, and didn't have a privacy cover or auto focus. The TECKNET is a big improvement in picture quality and sound clarity. The auto focus works great. It does not have a zoom lens, which I don't need, but would be the only additional feature I would want.
Facile da usare, si configura da sola e funziona immediatamente. CONSIGLIATISSIMO.
Spero che questo modello duri un po di più di 3 mesi .
Perfettamente compatibile con windows 10 e 11. Plug and play. Buona qualità immagine e suono.
